      "role": "user",
      "content": "the house is so quiet now. i keep waiting to hear his paws on the floor or the sound of his collar jingling but it just never happens. it's like the silence is actually heavy. i don't know why i'm even bothering to get up or do anything anymore. everything just feels so pointless without him.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
